LARDD 1
TITLE lardos-x86-mobile
TEXT LardOS for the 0.00001 percent sort of person with an x86-ISA phone, tablet, or handheld mobile PC.
SECTION Identity
ITEM Branch: lardos-x86-mobile
ITEM Version line: v3.0.0b-lardos-x86-mobile
ITEM Channel: beta
ITEM Architecture: x86/x86_64 ISA
SECTION What Changes
ITEM Mobile-first guidance for compact screens, touch/compact pointer input, and battery-aware operation.
ITEM Keeps the existing x86 boot media path so ISO/IMG artifacts are real x86 LardOS media.
ITEM Adds distro_guide.lardd inside the OS for local self-description.
SECTION What Does Not Change
ITEM No feature loss from main LardOS.
ITEM GUI, L-DOS, RXE, SYSRXE, SUM, KMO, media, recovery, native formats, and raw-control paths remain available.
ITEM The user still owns the machine; mobile defaults must stay visible and editable.
END
